{"tid":24553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Pizza Hut電單車與拖車相撞 食物速遞員傷重身亡","createTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T06:41:20.000Z","uid":38376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03f443bce769439a607106826a4941d052e06e82","tid":24553,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"葵涌晚上發生奪命車禍，一輛Pizza Hut電單車與拖車相撞，食物速遞員被拋出重創，送院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發晚上8時許，一名年約20多歲男子駕駛的Pizza Hut外送食物電單車，沿葵福路往葵涌方向駛至近盛福街交界時，與一輛拖車發生猛烈碰撞，食物速遞員被拋出，其後送院搶救，終重傷不治。<br />\n<br />\n涉事車司機沒有受傷，事發被帶上警車接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161205/s00001/1480946980870#sthash.kf7CuUuY.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161205%2Fs00001%2F1480946980870%23sthash.kf7CuUuY.dpuf&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=cc9d17d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161205%2Fs00001%2F1480946980870%23sthash.kf7CuUuY.dpuf&h=2995f992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161205/s00001/1480946980870#sthash.kf7CuUuY.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"9ae327863ae141c0fc2754be89fb24a124fedc31","tid":24553,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"Pizza仔好慘，自僱人士冇保險，公司又唔賠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e53388330a71b732d3eac30f4b8174e94db2d40","tid":24553,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"電單車真係好撚危險 就算唔會自炒都會比其他車撞 唔死都重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75019840123f927647558f1766749a9ef08e22fd","tid":24553,"uid":14131,"like":0,"disli